Symbol.Script_3D:
! Sidewall Exhaust Fan
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
addStatus1 = 0 addStatus3 = 0 IF GLOB_CONTEXT > 40 AND GLOB_CONTEXT < 50 THEN addStatus1 = 1 addStatus3 = 3 ENDIF
! --- HOTSPOT --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT -footSize/2, 0, footSize/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -footSize/2, 0, -footSize/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT footSize/2, 0, -footSize/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT footSize/2, 0, footSize/2, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
ROTx -90 ADD -footSize/2, -footSize/2, 0 BLOCK footSize, footSize, footHeight DEL 1
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ADDz footHeight MUL A/0.70, A/0.70, (B-footHeight)/0.55 CYLIND 0.10, 0.20 ADDz 0.10 ROTy -90 REVOLVE 11, 360, addStatus3, 0, 0.20, 0, 0.01414213562373, 0.2058578643763, 1, 0.02, 0.22, 1, 0.02, 0.2295429313288, 1, 0.02282370089659, 0.2525327091355, 1, 0.03109541695799, 0.2740965051983, 1, 0.04437118759079, 0.2930769447206, 1, 0.06184558224306, 0.3082805200201, 1, 0.08241669792557, 0.31878041463, 1, 0.1049804391087, 0.3240130768752, 1, 0.35, 0.35, 0 DEL 1 CYLIND 0.12, 0.13 ADDz 0.12 ROTy -90 REVOLVE 5, 360, addStatus1+2, 0, 0.20, 0, 0.23, 0.21, 0, 0.3161650008843, 0.1820800847737, 1, 0.3261755991803, 0.1748162046437, 1, 0.33, 0.1630539773395, 1 DEL 5 ELSE ADDz footHeight MUL A/0.70, A/0.70, (B-footHeight)/0.55 CYLIND 0.12, 0.20 ADDz 0.12 CONE 0.33, 0.30, 0.35, 90, 90 ADDz 0.33 CONE 0.10, 0.21, 0.18, 90, 90 DEL 4 ENDIF DEL 1
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1
DEL TOP
END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Sidewall Exhaust Fan
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 -footSize/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -footSize/2, footHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 footSize/2, footHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 footSize/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
PUT -footSize/2, 0, 1, -footSize/2, footHeight, 1, footSize/2, footHeight, 1, footSize/2, 0, 1, -footSize/2, 0, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
ADD2 0, footHeight MUL2 A/0.70, (B-footHeight)/0.55
HOTSPOT2 -0.35, 0.45, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0.35, 0.45, unID: unID=unID+1
LINE2 -0.35, 0.45, 0.35, 0.45 LINE2 -0.22, 0.12, 0.22, 0.12
FOR i = 1 TO 2 MUL2 1-2*(i-1), 1 POLY2_B 12, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, -0.2, 0, 1, -0.2, 0.10, 1, -0.22, 0.12, 1001, -0.2295429313288, 0.12, 1, -0.3240130768752, 0.2049804391087, 1001, -0.35, 0.45, 1, -0.21, 0.45, 1, -0.1820800847737, 0.5361650008843, 1, -0.1630539773395, 0.55, 1001, 0, 0.55, 0, 0, 0, 1 DEL 1 NEXT i
DEL 2 ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1 = ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1 DEL 1
END

call "FM_types_MEP" parameters DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 1 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval

Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF

IF B < A*0.30 THEN B = A*0.30 VALUES "B" RANGE [A*0.30,]

PARAMETERS ConPosX_1 = 0 PARAMETERS ConPosY_1 = 0 PARAMETERS ConPosZ_1 = 0 ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF setProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
